com.marklogic.client.qconsole.impl

Class DefaultWorkspaceManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.marklogic.client.helper.LoggingObject
      • com.marklogic.client.qconsole.impl.DefaultWorkspaceManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    WorkspaceManager

    public class DefaultWorkspaceManager
extends LoggingObject
implements WorkspaceManager
    Default implementation that uses the ML Java Client API to manage workspaces. By default, workspaces will be exported and imported to/from ~/.qconsole/workspaces/(ML username).
